[ SNIFFS ]

00:30.664 --> 00:31.998
I SMELL HIM ON YOU.

00:31.998 --> 00:33.033
CAN I HELP YOU?

00:33.033 --> 00:35.301
Y'ALL ARE LOOKING
FOR MY DAUGHTER.

00:35.301 --> 00:38.071
SO, WHAT'S
YOUR DAUGHTER'S NAME?

00:38.071 --> 00:39.640
[ TELEPHONE RINGS ]

00:39.640 --> 00:41.207
CANDACE YOUNG.

00:42.375 --> 00:44.144
CANDACE YOUNG?
MM‐HMM.

00:46.146 --> 00:47.313
WAIT HERE, PLEASE.

00:52.553 --> 00:54.621
SO THIS IS THE M.E. REPORT?

00:54.621 --> 00:56.757
YEAH.
IT LOOKS PRETTY BAD.

00:56.757 --> 00:58.358
DAMN.

00:58.358 --> 01:00.393
YOU KNOW YOU'RE GONNA
MAKE DETECTIVE.

01:00.393 --> 01:02.636
YEAH.
I HOPE SO.

01:02.636 --> 01:03.737
YOU WILL.

01:03.737 --> 01:05.371
THANKS.

01:05.371 --> 01:08.108
HEY. YOU KNOW MY SON
JUST WENT TO PRIVATE SCHOOL.

01:08.108 --> 01:10.476
[ CHUCKLES ]
WELL, I WON'T SAY ANYTHING.

01:10.476 --> 01:13.747
[ SIGHS ]
THANK YOU.

01:13.747 --> 01:15.716
LISTEN.
I'M SORRY I SHOT AT HIM.

01:17.350 --> 01:18.384
DON'T WORRY ABOUT IT.

01:18.384 --> 01:19.686
I THOUGHT HE WAS
ATTACKING YOU.

01:19.686 --> 01:21.121
YEAH, WELL, HE WASN'T.

01:21.121 --> 01:22.488
WHAT WAS GOING ON?

01:22.488 --> 01:24.090
NOTHING.
WE WERE JUST KIDDING AROUND.

01:24.090 --> 01:25.391
YOU SURE?

01:25.391 --> 01:27.260
[ FOLDER THUDS ]
WHAT DID IT LOOK LIKE?

01:27.260 --> 01:29.930
IT LOOKED LIKE HE WAS
GETTING THE BEST OF YOU.

01:29.930 --> 01:32.165
AND YOU THINK I WOULD
LET THAT HAPPEN?

01:32.165 --> 01:33.499
THAT'S THE ONLY
REASON I SHOT.

01:33.499 --> 01:35.401
I DIDN'T KNOW
HE WAS YOUR FRIEND.

01:35.401 --> 01:37.237
MY FRIEND?

01:37.237 --> 01:39.272
YEAH.

01:39.272 --> 01:40.574
HE'S NOT MY FRIEND.

01:40.574 --> 01:42.609
YOU SAID YOU TWO
WERE HORSING AROUND, SO...

01:42.609 --> 01:44.477
HE'S NOT MY FRIEND.

01:45.512 --> 01:46.747
YOU KNOW WHAT?
JUST DROP IT, OKAY?

01:46.747 --> 01:47.948
OKAY. OKAY.

01:47.948 --> 01:52.152
LOOK, YOU NEED TO KNOW
THAT IF HE REPORTS THIS,

01:52.152 --> 01:53.854
YOU'RE GONNA GET
IN A LOT OF TROUBLE.

01:53.854 --> 01:56.322
I KNOW.
CAN YOU TALK TO HIM?

01:58.224 --> 01:59.459
YEAH.
JUST LET ME HANDLE IT.

01:59.459 --> 02:01.101
I OWE YOU.

02:01.101 --> 02:02.102
YOU'RE DAMN RIGHT YOU DO.

02:02.102 --> 02:03.136
LISTEN.

02:03.136 --> 02:04.838
I DON'T KNOW
WHAT CAME OVER ME,

02:04.838 --> 02:06.339
BUT...THANKS.

02:06.339 --> 02:07.473
YEAH.
YOU GOT IT.

02:07.473 --> 02:10.176
HEY.
HAVE YOU SEEN BILLY?

02:10.176 --> 02:12.846
HE WENT HOME FOR THE DAY.

02:12.846 --> 02:14.214
CAN YOU HANDLE THIS?

02:14.214 --> 02:15.649
WHAT?

02:15.649 --> 02:17.383
THERE'S A LADY HERE
WHO SAYS SHE KNOWS

02:17.383 --> 02:18.852
WHERE CANDACE YOUNG IS.

02:18.852 --> 02:20.521
REALLY?
YEAH.

02:20.521 --> 02:23.957
I WAS SUPPOSED TO GET
THE DETECTIVE, BUT HE'S GONE.

02:23.957 --> 02:25.491
YEAH. UH, YEAH.
LET ME HANDLE IT.

02:25.491 --> 02:26.693
‐THANKS FOR TELLING ME.
‐MM‐HMM.

