[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

02:43.243 --> 02:44.611
[ TELEPHONE RINGS ]

02:44.611 --> 02:45.879
IS THIS HER?
YEAH.

02:48.114 --> 02:49.816
HI.

02:49.816 --> 02:51.251
HI.

02:51.251 --> 02:53.286
YOU ARE?

02:53.286 --> 02:54.855
HANNA YOUNG.

02:54.855 --> 02:56.990
AND YOU KNOW
WHERE CANDACE YOUNG IS?

02:56.990 --> 02:59.826
YES.

02:59.826 --> 03:01.134
WHERE?

03:03.203 --> 03:04.370
HOW WILL Y'ALL DO THIS?

03:04.370 --> 03:06.607
I'M SORRY?

03:08.374 --> 03:10.711
HOW WILL Y'ALL,
UH, ARREST HER?

03:10.711 --> 03:15.448
UM, WE'LL SEND OFFICERS.

03:15.448 --> 03:19.820
I MEAN, BUT WILL YOU COME WITH,
UM, GUNS AND STUFF LIKE THAT?

03:19.820 --> 03:22.388
WELL, THAT DEPENDS.
DOES SHE HAVE WEAPONS?

03:22.388 --> 03:24.490
NO. I DON'T ‐‐
I DON'T THINK SO.

03:24.490 --> 03:27.861
OKAY. THEN WE'LL JUST
ASK HER TO COME WITH US.

03:29.863 --> 03:32.833
OKAY, WELL...
WHY ARE YOU ASKING THIS?

03:35.301 --> 03:37.337
I HAVE HER SON.

03:37.337 --> 03:39.740
MY GRANDBABY.

03:39.740 --> 03:41.107
AND THAT BABY DON'T NEED
TO SEE ALL OF THAT.

03:41.107 --> 03:42.475
I UNDERSTAND.

03:42.475 --> 03:45.045
AND I DON'T KNOW HOW Y'ALL
DO WHAT YOU GOT TO DO,

03:45.045 --> 03:47.748
BUT MAYBE YOU CAN, LIKE,
WAIT FOR HER OUTSIDE.

03:49.115 --> 03:52.018
I'LL TALK TO THE BOSS,
AND I'M SURE WE CAN DO THAT.

03:52.018 --> 03:53.920
OKAY.

03:53.920 --> 03:56.757
I'M SURE SHE'LL
PROBABLY LEAVE ANYWAY.

03:56.757 --> 03:59.225
IS THERE ANY WAY YOU CAN
ENTICE HER OUT THE DOOR?

03:59.225 --> 04:02.703
IF I HAVE TO, YEAH.

04:02.703 --> 04:04.871
OKAY.
SO, WHERE IS SHE?

04:08.341 --> 04:10.410
THE FOUNTAIN DROP HOTEL.

04:10.410 --> 04:12.979
ON FOUNTAIN AND DUBLIN?

04:12.979 --> 04:14.715
YEAH.

04:14.715 --> 04:16.282
WHAT ROOM?

04:16.282 --> 04:17.718
LISTEN,
I'VE GOT TO BE SURE THAT Y'ALL

04:17.718 --> 04:18.785
ARE NOT
GONNA COME UP IN THERE

04:18.785 --> 04:20.386
AND JUST RAID THE PLACE
AND ALL THAT.

04:20.386 --> 04:22.689
THAT BABY...
NO, MA'AM. WE WON'T DO THAT.

04:24.891 --> 04:26.159
YOU SURE?

04:26.159 --> 04:27.193
YES.

04:27.193 --> 04:29.129
WE'LL WAIT FOR HER
TO COME OUTSIDE,

04:29.129 --> 04:30.964
AND THEN WE'LL TAKE
HER INTO CUSTODY.

04:33.033 --> 04:34.901
WHAT'S THE ROOM NUMBER?

04:34.901 --> 04:38.204
17.

04:38.204 --> 04:40.907
OKAY.
WE'LL SEND AN OFFICER OVER.

04:40.907 --> 04:41.908
WHAT? NOW?

04:41.908 --> 04:43.577
YEAH.
NO, NO, NO, NO.

04:43.577 --> 04:45.111
THE BABY HAS TO GO
TO SCHOOL IN THE MORNING.

04:45.111 --> 04:47.347
I MEAN, CAN YOU ‐‐

04:47.347 --> 04:49.883
CAN YOU WAIT UNTIL I PUT HIM
ON THE SCHOOL BUS?

04:49.883 --> 04:51.284
AND MAYBE Y'ALL CAN
DO IT AFTER THAT?

04:51.284 --> 04:54.287
I'LL TALK TO THE BOSS
ABOUT SETTING UP SURVEILLANCE.

04:54.287 --> 04:56.422
OKAY.
THANK YOU.

04:56.422 --> 04:58.992
CAN YOU CALL US
TO VERIFY SHE'S THERE?

04:58.992 --> 05:00.126
YES.

05:00.126 --> 05:02.869
AND THEN WE'LL SIT OUTSIDE
AND WAIT FOR HER.

05:02.869 --> 05:04.605
OKAY. THANK YOU.
SURE.

05:04.605 --> 05:06.940
UM, WHO ARE YOU TO HER?

05:10.143 --> 05:12.378
HER MOTHER.

05:12.378 --> 05:14.881
♪♪♪♪

05:14.881 --> 05:16.917
OKAY.

05:18.852 --> 05:21.087
MS. YOUNG?

05:21.087 --> 05:22.255
CAN I ASK YOU A QUESTION?

05:22.255 --> 05:24.224
YEAH, WHAT ‐‐

05:24.224 --> 05:26.960
WHAT IS IT?

05:26.960 --> 05:29.395
DO YOU KNOW
HOW QUINCY MAXWELL DIED?

05:29.395 --> 05:30.997
NO.

05:30.997 --> 05:33.166
YOUR DAUGHTER
DIDN'T MENTION ANYTHING?

05:33.166 --> 05:34.467
NO, SHE DIDN'T.

05:35.802 --> 05:37.137
WELL, JUST SO YOU KNOW,

05:37.137 --> 05:39.740
HE WAS STABBED OVER 40 TIMES,
ACCORDING TO THE M.E.

05:41.474 --> 05:44.344
DO YOU KNOW HOW
THEIR RELATIONSHIP WAS?

05:44.344 --> 05:46.112
IT WASN'T GOOD.

05:46.112 --> 05:47.380
I MEAN,
LOOK AT HIS RECORD.

05:47.380 --> 05:51.585
I'M TELLING YOU,
THAT BOY WAS [SCOFFS] BAD NEWS.

05:51.585 --> 05:55.055
HOW BAD?
LOOK AT HIS RECORD.

05:55.055 --> 05:56.590
OKAY.

05:56.590 --> 05:58.859
UM, DO YOU MIND ELABORATING

05:58.859 --> 06:00.567
ON YOUR DAUGHTER'S
RELATIONSHIP WITH HIM?

06:02.268 --> 06:04.404
LOOK, ALL I CAN SAY

06:04.404 --> 06:08.441
IS THAT HE WAS VERY,
VERY VIOLENT TO HER AND HER SON.

06:08.441 --> 06:10.110
HIS OWN SON, NOW.

06:10.110 --> 06:12.779
I DON'T KNOW, BUT IF SHE DID
ANYTHING TO HIM,

06:12.779 --> 06:14.180
IT WAS PROBABLY
IN SELF‐DEFENSE,

06:14.180 --> 06:16.416
AND SHE WAS PROBABLY TRYING
TO GET AWAY FROM HIM.

06:16.416 --> 06:17.551
SO, IS THAT WHY SHE KILLED HIM?

06:17.551 --> 06:19.319
I DIDN'T SAY SHE KILLED HIM.
HOLD UP. WAIT, WAIT.

06:19.319 --> 06:20.954
BUT, YOU JUST SAID THAT ‐‐
NO, I SAID

06:20.954 --> 06:22.155
IF SHE DID
ANYTHING TO HIM,

06:22.155 --> 06:23.857
IT WAS PROBABLY
IN SELF‐DEFENSE

06:23.857 --> 06:25.458
AND THAT SHE WAS PROBABLY
TRYING TO GET AWAY.

06:25.458 --> 06:26.860
NOW, THAT'S ‐‐ THOSE
ARE TWO DIFFERENT THINGS.

06:26.860 --> 06:28.428
MS. YOUNG. MS. YOUNG.
WHAT? WHAT?

06:28.428 --> 06:30.864
THERE IS NO NEED TO GET UPSET.
I'M JUST ASKING QUESTIONS.

06:30.864 --> 06:32.733
WELL, THAT'S WHY I TOLD YOU
WHERE SHE WAS ‐‐

06:32.733 --> 06:33.800
SO YOU CAN GO ASK HER.

06:33.800 --> 06:35.068
WE WILL.
OKAY.

06:35.068 --> 06:36.737
PLEASE.

06:36.737 --> 06:38.238
MS. YOUNG.

06:38.238 --> 06:39.305
DO YOU KNOW WHO ELSE
WOULD'VE HELPED HER?

06:39.305 --> 06:41.207
NO, I DON'T.
LOOK.

06:41.207 --> 06:43.309
YOU TOLD ME THAT
YOUR DAUGHTER DIDN'T KILL HIM.

06:43.309 --> 06:44.978
I'M CLEAR ON THAT.
MM‐HMM.

06:44.978 --> 06:46.446
HOWEVER, THE M.E. SAID

06:46.446 --> 06:48.649
THAT THERE HAD TO BE
MORE THAN ONE ASSAILANT.

06:48.649 --> 06:50.350
SOME OF THE STAB WOUNDS

06:50.350 --> 06:52.653
CAME FROM HIGHER
AND THEY WERE DEEPER,

06:52.653 --> 06:54.487
LIKE THERE WERE
TWO DIFFERENT PEOPLE.

06:54.487 --> 06:56.256
AND THE MEDICAL EXAMINER
SEEMS TO THINK

06:56.256 --> 06:57.357
THAT THERE WAS
A MALE INVOLVED.

06:57.357 --> 06:59.125
DO YOU KNOW WHO
THAT MIGHT'VE BEEN?

06:59.125 --> 07:00.634
NO, I DON'T.

07:00.634 --> 07:02.536
OKAY.

07:04.170 --> 07:05.839
THAT'S MY CARD.

07:05.839 --> 07:07.273
CAN YOU TEXT ME
WHEN YOU GET THERE

07:07.273 --> 07:09.242
JUST TO VERIFY SHE'S THERE?

07:09.242 --> 07:11.377
YEAH.
AND I'LL CALL MY BOSS.

07:12.345 --> 07:13.413
OKAY.

07:13.413 --> 07:14.447
ARE YOU HEADING THERE NOW?

07:14.447 --> 07:16.049
YEAH.
OKAY.

07:17.651 --> 07:19.352
YOU SAID Y'ALL
WOULDN'T DO IT TONIGHT.

07:19.352 --> 07:21.387
WE DON'T EVEN HAVE A WARRANT
TO GET INTO THE ROOM,

07:21.387 --> 07:24.124
SO WE HAVE TO WAIT
FOR YOUR CONFIRMATION

07:24.124 --> 07:25.792
TO VERIFY
THAT SHE'S THERE,

07:25.792 --> 07:27.794
SO WE'LL WAIT
FOR YOUR CALL

07:27.794 --> 07:29.563
UNLESS MY BOSS
GETS A WARRANT,

07:29.563 --> 07:31.765
WHICH THAT WON'T BE
UNTIL SOMETIME TOMORROW.

07:31.765 --> 07:35.035
SO, WE'LL BE WAITING
ON YOUR WORD, OKAY?

07:35.035 --> 07:36.436
OKAY.

07:39.372 --> 07:41.074
YOU DID THE RIGHT THING,
MS. YOUNG.

07:45.011 --> 07:47.047
♪♪♪♪

07:55.856 --> 07:57.991
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

08:03.670 --> 08:06.206
[ Ringing ]

08:06.206 --> 08:08.742
[ CELLPHONE RINGS ]

08:11.678 --> 08:14.581
[ CELLPHONE BEEPS ]

08:17.984 --> 08:20.020
♪♪♪♪

08:38.672 --> 08:40.707
[ BREATHING SHAKILY ]

08:54.821 --> 08:57.390
♪♪♪♪

08:57.390 --> 08:59.425
[ SIGHS ]

09:00.827 --> 09:03.003
I DON'T KNOW
IF I REALLY WANT IT.

09:03.003 --> 09:05.171
YOU'VE GOT TO BE KIDDING ME.

09:05.171 --> 09:06.773
[ CHUCKLES ]

09:06.773 --> 09:09.676
NO.
I'M NOT.

09:12.178 --> 09:15.015
ITS THE PRESIDENT
OF THE UNITED STATES.

09:15.015 --> 09:17.383
YEAH, I KNOW.

09:17.383 --> 09:20.053
[ SCOFFS ]

09:20.053 --> 09:23.456
DO YOU KNOW HOW MANY MEN
AND WOMEN HAVE DREAMT OF THAT?

09:23.456 --> 09:26.026
YEAH, BUT YOU DON'T KNOW
WHAT COMES WITH IT

09:26.026 --> 09:27.561
UNTIL YOU'RE IN IT.

09:27.561 --> 09:30.363
HMM.
IT CAN BE STIFLING.

09:30.363 --> 09:34.535
I MEAN,
IT CAN SUFFOCATE YOU.

09:34.535 --> 09:37.538
THAT BUBBLE IS SMALL.

09:38.905 --> 09:41.141
I'M SORRY, BUT YOU GET
NO SYMPATHY FROM ME TONIGHT.

09:41.141 --> 09:42.709
[ BOTH CHUCKLE ]

09:42.709 --> 09:44.277
LOOK.

09:44.277 --> 09:46.046
I'M A KID THAT GREW UP
IN DETROIT

09:46.046 --> 09:48.081
BY WAY OF TENNESSEE.
MM‐HMM.

09:48.081 --> 09:51.017
AND WHEN I'M IN THOSE ROOMS,
I JUST ‐‐

09:51.017 --> 09:52.819
I WANT TO SCREAM

09:52.819 --> 09:54.988
EVEN THOUGH I KNOW
HOW TO PLAY THE GAME.

09:54.988 --> 09:56.590
OBVIOUSLY.

09:56.590 --> 09:59.526
OBVIOUSLY,
IT'S DEBILITATING.

10:00.834 --> 10:03.804
I LOVE POLITICS.
I‐I DO.

10:03.804 --> 10:06.406
BUT THAT LIFE OF IT
IN THAT WHITE HOUSE,

10:06.406 --> 10:10.076
AND WITHOUT MY WIFE,
RAISING MY KIDS ALONE ‐‐

10:10.076 --> 10:11.177
[ SIGHS ]

10:11.177 --> 10:13.379
KIDS?

10:13.379 --> 10:15.015
7 AND 10.

10:15.015 --> 10:16.449
I DIDN'T KNOW THAT.

10:16.449 --> 10:18.118
YOU REALLY SHOULD
LOOK ME UP ON THE NET.

10:18.118 --> 10:20.787
[ CHUCKLES ]
I'M SORRY.

10:20.787 --> 10:24.024
I MEAN,
I AM A REALLY GOOD GUY.

10:24.024 --> 10:26.392
SO YOUR LIPS SAY.

10:26.392 --> 10:28.361
NO. I AM.

10:28.361 --> 10:30.263
OKAY.

10:30.263 --> 10:33.366
WELL, UM, I'LL MAKE SURE
MY CHIEF OF STAFF

10:33.366 --> 10:34.568
LOOKS YOU UP
WHEN I GET HOME.

10:34.568 --> 10:35.636
[ LAUGHS ]

10:35.636 --> 10:38.104
DO YOU WANT ANOTHER DRINK?

10:38.104 --> 10:39.272
YOU TRYING TO GET ME DRUNK?

10:39.272 --> 10:41.508
I'M TRYING TO MAKE YOU
STAY DRUNK.

10:43.443 --> 10:45.045
I WILL IF YOU WILL.

10:47.213 --> 10:48.815
YOU WILL?

10:48.815 --> 10:51.585
THE DRINK, THAT IS.

10:53.754 --> 10:56.757
IS THERE ANYTHING ELSE
YOU'LL DO?

10:56.757 --> 10:59.059
CANDACE.

10:59.059 --> 11:01.568
YES?

11:01.568 --> 11:03.804
THIS TAKES ME BACK
TO THAT BUBBLE.

11:03.804 --> 11:06.272
HOW SO?

11:06.272 --> 11:09.510
I'M GONNA BE PRESIDENT.

11:09.510 --> 11:12.546
I CAN'T JUST SLEEP WITH A WOMAN
I JUST MET AT A HOTEL.

11:14.414 --> 11:15.682
YOU'RE SINGLE, RIGHT?

11:15.682 --> 11:17.718
I'M A WIDOWER.

11:17.718 --> 11:21.154
WELL, SHE'S NOT HERE.

11:21.154 --> 11:24.357
YOU HAVE NEEDS,
DON'T YOU?

11:24.357 --> 11:26.693
YEAH.

11:26.693 --> 11:28.094
I DO.

11:28.094 --> 11:29.796
SO DO I.

11:36.102 --> 11:37.804
I CAN'T.

11:37.804 --> 11:41.608
[ SIGHS ]

11:41.608 --> 11:43.644
IS IT THE BUBBLE
OR YOUR WIFE?

11:43.644 --> 11:45.679
WHAT?

11:45.679 --> 11:49.149
WAS SHE THE ONLY ONE?

11:49.149 --> 11:51.885
YEAH.

11:51.885 --> 11:53.353
WELL, THEN YOU KNOW
IT'S YOUR WIFE

11:53.353 --> 11:54.988
AND NOT THE BUBBLE.

11:54.988 --> 11:58.024
I'VE ONLY BEEN WITH MY WIFE
FOR THE PAST 15 YEARS.

11:58.024 --> 12:01.535
AND I DON'T KNOW
HOW TO DO THIS.

12:04.871 --> 12:07.440
I'M NOT SURE I WANT
TO KNOW HOW TO DO THIS.

12:08.809 --> 12:11.377
IT'S LIKE...

12:11.377 --> 12:12.846
RIDING A BIKE?

12:14.047 --> 12:15.348
[ CHUCKLES ]

12:15.348 --> 12:17.283
RIDING SOMETHING.

12:20.353 --> 12:21.955
[ SIGHS ]
[ CHUCKLES ]

12:21.955 --> 12:23.857
[ LAUGHS ]

12:27.260 --> 12:29.362
YOU'RE VERY FORWARD.

12:30.363 --> 12:31.998
YOU DON'T LIKE
STRONG WOMEN?

12:31.998 --> 12:35.401
I LOVE STRONG WOMEN.

12:35.401 --> 12:36.970
AND BEAUTIFUL ONES.

12:36.970 --> 12:37.971
THANK YOU.

12:37.971 --> 12:39.372
YOU ARE.

12:39.372 --> 12:40.741
[ LAUGHS ]

12:40.741 --> 12:42.576
[ LAUGHS ]

12:42.576 --> 12:44.444
THANK YOU.

12:51.618 --> 12:53.754
BUT I CAN'T DO THIS.

12:53.754 --> 12:56.222
WHAT IF I TOLD YOU
I WASN'T INTERESTED

12:56.222 --> 13:01.367
IN EVER LETTING ANYONE KNOW
ABOUT THIS MOMENT?

13:01.367 --> 13:03.403
[ SCOFFS ]

13:05.371 --> 13:06.773
I'VE HEARD THAT BEFORE.

13:06.773 --> 13:09.175
SO, YOU HAVE HAD AFFAIRS.

13:09.175 --> 13:11.011
NO.

13:11.011 --> 13:13.780
FROM A FORMER FRIEND

13:13.780 --> 13:15.081
WHO USED TO SAY THAT.

13:16.482 --> 13:18.318
BUT THEN THEY USE IT
AGAINST YOU.

13:20.687 --> 13:23.423
HOW DO YOU KNOW I DON'T WANT
TO RUIN MY REPUTATION?

13:23.423 --> 13:27.093
HOW WOULD I RUIN
YOUR REPUTATION?

13:27.093 --> 13:28.995
[ SCOFFS ]
HELLO.

13:28.995 --> 13:31.064
NO, I DIDN'T MEAN THAT
AS AN INSULT.

13:31.064 --> 13:33.333
EXPLAIN YOURSELF.

13:33.333 --> 13:34.768
‐YOU'RE A WOMAN.
‐MM‐HMM.

13:34.768 --> 13:37.738
NO DOUBT, A STRONG ONE.

13:37.738 --> 13:40.340
I THINK YOU'D ACTUALLY HELP
MY REPUTATION.

13:40.340 --> 13:42.543
YOU TOTALLY
POLITICKED ME.

13:42.543 --> 13:44.177
WHAT?

13:44.177 --> 13:45.211
YEP.
NO.

13:45.211 --> 13:46.279
YEAH.
NO.

13:46.279 --> 13:49.583
YOU DIDN'T ANSWER
THE QUESTION.

13:49.583 --> 13:52.185
WELL, WHY DON'T YOU TELL ME
WHAT YOU MEAN?

13:52.185 --> 13:55.155
BEING THAT I AM
A FINAL‐YEAR LAW STUDENT,

13:55.155 --> 13:58.592
TO THIS POINT, I HAVE WORKED
FOR EVERYTHING THAT I HAVE.

13:58.592 --> 14:00.060
I WOULDN'T WANT TO WASTE IT

14:00.060 --> 14:04.270
BY SLEEPING WITH THE MOST
POWERFUL MAN IN THE WORLD,

14:04.270 --> 14:06.807
OR SOON‐TO‐BE.

14:06.807 --> 14:10.176
I'D WANT PEOPLE TO KNOW THAT
I WORKED FOR EVERYTHING I HAVE.

14:13.514 --> 14:14.948
I UNDERSTAND THAT.

14:17.183 --> 14:19.720
SO, I'M NOT INTERESTED

14:19.720 --> 14:25.592
IN EVER LETTING
THIS MOMENT BE KNOWN.

14:26.893 --> 14:28.662
YOU PROMISE?

14:28.662 --> 14:30.531
REAL PROMISE.

14:34.367 --> 14:36.970
WELL, I DO FIND YOU
IMPOSSIBLE TO RESIST.

14:36.970 --> 14:38.939
HMM.

14:38.939 --> 14:40.073
MOST OF THEM DO.

14:40.073 --> 14:43.109
♪♪♪♪

14:46.312 --> 14:50.016
ARE WE ACTUALLY
DOING THIS?

14:50.016 --> 14:51.351
MM‐HMM.

14:52.653 --> 14:54.988
AND THIS WON'T
COME BACK TO BITE ME?

14:54.988 --> 14:56.356
Shh.

14:59.092 --> 15:02.636
YOU JUST HAVE TO...
STOP THINKING

15:02.636 --> 15:06.372
ABOUT BEING
THE FUTURE PRESIDENT

15:06.372 --> 15:11.912
AND JUST BE CHARLES
FOR AN HOUR OR TWO.

15:11.912 --> 15:13.980
CANDACE.
MM.

15:46.446 --> 15:49.015
♪♪♪♪

16:57.724 --> 16:59.425
♪♪♪♪

16:59.425 --> 17:01.067
[ CELLPHONE CHIMES ]

17:08.308 --> 17:10.176
[ FOOTSTEPS APPROACHING ]

17:13.647 --> 17:15.582
I KNOW FOR SURE
THAT YOU HAVEN'T BEEN

17:15.582 --> 17:17.684
STANDING THERE
THIS WHOLE TIME.

17:20.386 --> 17:22.322
DO YOU WANT ME TO TAKE
THAT THING AWAY FROM YOU?

17:24.224 --> 17:26.627
GO ON IN THE ROOM, BOY.

17:36.703 --> 17:38.271
[ SIGHS ]

17:48.549 --> 17:50.250
HI.

17:52.285 --> 17:54.621
[ SIGHS ]

17:54.621 --> 17:56.657
YOU KNOW THAT DOES
NOTHING FOR ME, RIGHT?

17:56.657 --> 17:59.960
YEP.
STILL HER IDEA.

18:01.868 --> 18:03.904
[ CELLPHONE BEEPS ]

18:06.439 --> 18:09.475
[ LAUGHS ]
[ CELLPHONE BUZZING ]

18:09.475 --> 18:11.812
[ LAUGHS ]

18:13.179 --> 18:15.048
OH.

18:17.150 --> 18:18.785
YEAH, SO...

18:20.554 --> 18:22.422
[ BOTH CHUCKLING ]

18:22.422 --> 18:23.724
OHH.

18:23.724 --> 18:25.158
HEY, IT'S ME.

18:25.158 --> 18:26.560
YOUR MOM WENT TO THE POLICE
AND TOLD THEM WHERE YOU ARE,

18:26.560 --> 18:28.228
SO CAN YOU PLEASE CALL ME BACK?

18:28.228 --> 18:29.930
BYE.

18:29.930 --> 18:31.364
[ CELLPHONE BEEPS ]

18:31.364 --> 18:34.267
[ SIGHS ]
WHAT'S GOING ON?

18:35.536 --> 18:37.303
WHO ARE YOU
TO ASK ME ANYTHING?

18:37.303 --> 18:41.041
