I JUST WANTED TO KNOW.

18:41.041 --> 18:44.545
YOU SEEM BOTHERED.
YOU WANT TO TELL ME WHY?

18:44.545 --> 18:47.781
THE PERSON LAYING IN THE BED
IS WHY I'M BOTHERED.

18:47.781 --> 18:49.449
WHAT'S REALLY GOING ON?

18:52.118 --> 18:55.622
YOU.
THIS.

18:55.622 --> 18:57.090
THIS IS MY PROBLEM.

18:57.090 --> 18:59.893
NO. THERE'S SOMETHING ELSE.
I CAN TELL.

18:59.893 --> 19:01.735
OH, PLEASE.
YOU CAN'T TELL...

19:03.704 --> 19:06.973
WHY ARE YOU SO AGGRAVATED?
WHAT'S GOING ON?

19:06.973 --> 19:12.345
I GOT IN A FIGHT WITH MY LOVER.
THAT'S...WHAT'S GOING ON.

19:12.345 --> 19:14.114
WAS IT BAD?

19:14.114 --> 19:15.649
REALLY?

19:15.649 --> 19:17.584
I MEAN, ARE YOU ACTING
LIKE YOU CARE RIGHT NOW?

19:17.584 --> 19:19.419
IS THAT IT?
NO, I'M NOT ACTING.

19:19.419 --> 19:21.054
THEN WHAT THE HELL
ARE YOU DOING?

19:21.054 --> 19:24.758
[ SIGHS ] I DON'T CARE.
WHATEVER. FORGET IT.

19:24.758 --> 19:26.192
THANK YOU.

19:31.898 --> 19:33.567
SO, WAS THAT HIM ‐‐

19:33.567 --> 19:35.536
THAT OFFICER OUTSIDE ‐‐

19:35.536 --> 19:36.870
THE LOVER THAT
PISSED YOU OFF?

19:36.870 --> 19:38.071
TRUST ME,
I DON'T NEED A REASON

19:38.071 --> 19:39.973
TO BE PISSED OFF
WHEN I WALK IN HERE.

19:39.973 --> 19:43.644
I SAW YOUR BODY LANGUAGE
WHILE YOU WERE TALKING TO HIM.

19:43.644 --> 19:45.345
IT SEEMED INTERESTING.

19:47.047 --> 19:49.382
SO YOU'RE AN EXPERT
ON BODY LANGUAGE NOW?

19:49.382 --> 19:52.385
NO.
I JUST WATCH.

19:52.385 --> 19:55.221
AND I WAS WATCHING YOU.

19:55.221 --> 19:58.458
IT DIDN'T SEEM LIKE
AN OFFICER TALKING TO YOU.

19:58.458 --> 20:00.627
IT SEEMED LIKE
SOMETHING CASUAL.

20:00.627 --> 20:04.671
SOMETHING...
YES, MELISSA.

20:04.671 --> 20:07.173
HE WAS MY LOVER.

20:07.173 --> 20:09.876
OH. OKAY.

20:09.876 --> 20:12.846
YES, AND WE HAD
JUST HAD SEX.

20:12.846 --> 20:14.414
OKAY.

20:14.414 --> 20:16.149
YEAH?
THAT'S OKAY?

20:16.149 --> 20:18.484
AND IT WAS GOOD.

20:18.484 --> 20:20.386
OKAY.

20:20.386 --> 20:25.491
AND HE WAS SWEATING
AND CALLING MY NAME.

20:25.491 --> 20:29.596
AND HE WAS TOUCHING ME
AND LICKING ME.

20:29.596 --> 20:30.597
SPARE ME THE DETAILS.

20:30.597 --> 20:32.265
NO, NO, NO, NO.
LET'S TALK.

20:32.265 --> 20:33.567
COME ON. TALK ABOUT IT.
JEFFERY.

20:33.567 --> 20:34.901
NO, NO, NO, NO.
NO.

20:34.901 --> 20:40.440
HE GRABBED ME FIRST
AND PULLED ME INTO HIS CHEST.

20:40.440 --> 20:45.846
AND IT WAS SO HARD,
HIS BODY UNDER THAT UNIFORM.

20:45.846 --> 20:47.814
SO HOT.

20:47.814 --> 20:50.350
AND HIS ASS
WAS LIKE STEEL.

20:50.350 --> 20:51.451
JEFFERY.

20:51.451 --> 20:52.519
ALL RIGHT.

20:52.519 --> 20:55.922
AND THEN
I WAS SO TURNED ON.

20:59.392 --> 21:01.334
RIGHT?

21:01.334 --> 21:03.670
JUST LIKE NOW.

21:03.670 --> 21:05.471
AND THAT'S NOT FOR YOU.

21:07.340 --> 21:09.042
IT'LL NEVER BE FOR YOU.

21:09.042 --> 21:11.444
SO, WHERE WAS I?

21:14.080 --> 21:18.418
THEN HE GRABBED ME,
CLIMBED ON TOP OF ME.

21:18.418 --> 21:20.420
I WAS SO READY.

21:20.420 --> 21:21.988
AND...

21:25.091 --> 21:27.661
Veronica:
AND THEN WHAT HAPPENED?

21:27.661 --> 21:30.096
GO ON.
FINISH.

21:30.096 --> 21:31.965
SO, YOU'RE STANDING
IN THE DOORWAY NOW?

21:31.965 --> 21:34.801
NO, I WAS GOING DOWNSTAIRS
TO GET ANOTHER DRINK,

21:34.801 --> 21:36.837
AND I HEARD YOU
TELLING YOUR STORY.

21:36.837 --> 21:38.471
SO, GO ON.

21:38.471 --> 21:39.540
FINISH.

21:39.540 --> 21:42.843
‐HE WAS FINISHED.
‐NO, MELISSA. HE WASN'T.

21:42.843 --> 21:45.679
NOW, GO ON, FINISH TELLING
YOUR FUTURE WIFE

21:45.679 --> 21:49.215
ABOUT THE NASTY‐ASS MEN'S SWEAT
THAT YOU LIKE ON YOUR BODY.

21:49.215 --> 21:51.785
HE WAS...
MELISSA.

21:51.785 --> 21:54.721
BITCH, I WAS NOT
TALKING TO YOU.

21:54.721 --> 21:56.790
SORRY.

21:59.025 --> 22:00.567
ARE YOU SURE
YOU'RE READY FOR IT?

22:00.567 --> 22:02.435
YES.

22:02.435 --> 22:04.270
I WANT TO HEAR
HOW LOW YOU CAN GO.

22:04.270 --> 22:06.973
OH, I CAN GO
AS LOW AS YOU CAN.

22:06.973 --> 22:08.742
[ CHUCKLES ]

22:08.742 --> 22:09.810
MELISSA, I LIKE IT

22:09.810 --> 22:11.812
WHEN A QUEEN TRIES
TO COME FOR ME.

22:11.812 --> 22:14.380
MS. HONEY?

22:14.380 --> 22:16.583
YES, MISS THANG?

22:16.583 --> 22:18.151
MISS HONEY, YOU WORK.

22:18.151 --> 22:20.386
[ SNAPPING FINGERS ]
YOU WORK, MISS THANG.

22:20.386 --> 22:22.923
YOU SLAY!
ISN'T THAT IT?

22:22.923 --> 22:24.858
HUH?
ISN'T THAT IT?

22:24.858 --> 22:26.259
YOU KNOW HOW YOU GET
WHEN YOU'VE BEEN DRINKING.

22:26.259 --> 22:29.663
WHY DON'T YOU GO BACK
TO YOUR BED AND SLEEP IT OFF?

22:29.663 --> 22:31.832
THE MOST IMPORTANT THING

22:31.832 --> 22:33.800
IS THAT
THAT GIRL INSIDE YOU

22:33.800 --> 22:37.403
KNOW I GET
WHEN I'VE BEEN DRINKING.

22:37.403 --> 22:40.774
WELL, MAYBE YOU SHOULD
CARVE HER OUT.

22:40.774 --> 22:42.475
IS THAT A REFERENCE

22:42.475 --> 22:45.979
TO THE PARING KNIFE
YOU PUT IN MY CHEST?

22:45.979 --> 22:49.550
YOU KNOW, MELISSA,
JEFFERY IS GOING TO THE DA

22:49.550 --> 22:51.518
TO TESTIFY AGAINST ME.

22:51.518 --> 22:55.556
SOMETHING TO DO
WITH WYATT CRYER.

22:55.556 --> 22:58.792
THAT'S WHY I HAD
TO CANCEL THE ENGAGEMENT PARTY.

22:58.792 --> 23:02.035
HE'S TRIED ALL SORTS OF THINGS
TO PUT ME AWAY.

23:02.035 --> 23:06.406
EVEN PUT A KNIFE
IN MY CHEST.

23:06.406 --> 23:08.474
[ Singsong voice ]
I'M STILL HERE.

23:08.474 --> 23:10.811
[ Normal voice ]
SEE, WHAT YOU DON'T
UNDERSTAND, SON,

23:10.811 --> 23:14.014
IS I WILL ALWAYS BE HERE.

23:15.916 --> 23:19.085
NOW, I DON'T KNOW WHAT WAS
GOING ON DOWN THERE

23:19.085 --> 23:22.122
BETWEEN YOU
AND OFFICER TOO FRIENDLY,

23:22.122 --> 23:24.625
BUT I'LL TELL YOU THIS ‐‐

23:24.625 --> 23:27.828
THAT IS OVER.

23:27.828 --> 23:30.396
NOW, THIS...

23:30.396 --> 23:32.432
THIS IS YOUR FUTURE, SON.

23:35.401 --> 23:37.137
I THINK YOU SHOULD.

23:37.137 --> 23:39.205
WHAT?

23:39.205 --> 23:42.809
I THINK IF HE WANTS
TO BE WITH HIM, HE SHOULD.

23:42.809 --> 23:44.711
YOU THINK?

23:44.711 --> 23:46.847
YES.

23:54.387 --> 23:57.323
IS THAT SOMETHING
NEW FOR YOU, DEAR ‐‐

23:57.323 --> 23:59.392
YOU THINKING?

24:02.102 --> 24:04.505
[ LAUGHS ]

24:06.540 --> 24:09.543
THAT'S HILARIOUS.

24:09.543 --> 24:11.344
YOU DON'T THINK.

24:11.344 --> 24:14.280
YOU DO AS I TELL YOU.

24:14.280 --> 24:16.116
YOU'RE LIKE THIS WALLPAPER
OR THE FURNITURE ‐‐

24:16.116 --> 24:18.184
YOU'RE BOUGHT AND PAID FOR.

24:18.184 --> 24:20.220
NOW, YOU DON'T HAVE
ANOTHER THOUGHT.

24:20.220 --> 24:21.487
YOU WILL CARRY MY GRANDCHILD,

24:21.487 --> 24:24.190
AND YOU WILL DO IT WELL,
BUT YOU WILL NOT THINK.

24:29.095 --> 24:31.698
Jeffery,
did she say she thinks?

24:31.698 --> 24:35.035
[ LAUGHS ]

24:35.035 --> 24:37.370
YOU.

24:37.370 --> 24:38.872
AH.

24:38.872 --> 24:40.807
ALL RIGHT.

24:40.807 --> 24:44.545
NOW, JEFFERY, I DON'T WANT YOU
TO SEE THAT MAN AGAIN, OKAY?

24:44.545 --> 24:46.379
LISTEN TO ME.

24:46.379 --> 24:48.014
LISTEN TO YOU?

24:48.014 --> 24:50.083
YES.

24:50.083 --> 24:55.055
I'M HERE, WHICH MEANS
THAT YOU NEED TO LET THIS GO.

24:55.055 --> 24:56.957
I'VE DONE ALL
YOUR RIDICULOUS RULES.

24:56.957 --> 25:00.927
I ‐‐ I'M ‐‐

25:00.927 --> 25:02.636
WHY DON'T YOU GO BACK
TO YOUR BED AND SLEEP IT OFF

25:02.636 --> 25:04.170
AND JUST LEAVE ME ALONE?

25:04.170 --> 25:06.139
I'M NOT SCARED OF YOU.

25:06.139 --> 25:09.309
I'M NOT SCARED OF YOU.
I AM NOT AFRAID OF YOU!

25:12.613 --> 25:14.347
NOT WHEN YOU'RE DRINKING,
ANYWAY.

25:14.347 --> 25:15.749
BOY, I WILL COME OVER THERE ‐‐

25:15.749 --> 25:18.885
BOBBY SAFEMAN.

25:28.729 --> 25:30.196
JEFFERY...

25:32.498 --> 25:36.369
...I AM NOT TRYING
TO HURT YOU.

25:36.369 --> 25:38.304
I'M NOT TRYING
TO DESTROY YOUR LIFE.

25:38.304 --> 25:41.241
I'M JUST TRYING TO MAKE
YOUR LIFE BETTER,

25:41.241 --> 25:42.909
LIKE ANY PARENT WOULD.

25:44.778 --> 25:46.980
BY LOCKING ME UP IN HERE
WITH HER?

25:46.980 --> 25:50.216
I'M NOT LOCKING
YOU UP ANYWHERE.

25:50.216 --> 25:51.685
HONEY, YOU WILL LEARN
TO LOVE THIS.

25:51.685 --> 25:52.853
YOU'VE JUST GOT TO TRY IT.

25:52.853 --> 25:55.255
YOU'VE GOT TO TRY IT
A FEW MORE TIMES.

25:55.255 --> 25:57.157
SHE'S NOT
A BAD‐LOOKING GIRL.

25:57.157 --> 25:58.725
SHE'S GOT
A FEW STRETCH MARKS.

25:58.725 --> 26:00.160
SHE'S NOT QUITE
DARK ENOUGH.

26:00.160 --> 26:02.569
SHE DON'T HAVE NO BREASTS,
AND SHE WHINES ALL THE TIME.

26:02.569 --> 26:05.238
BUT EVERYBODY CAN'T BE
PERFECT LIKE YOUR MOTHER.

26:06.873 --> 26:08.374
NOW, I HAVE GIVEN YOU
THIS FREEDOM.

26:08.374 --> 26:09.810
YOU NEED TO HONOR IT.

26:09.810 --> 26:12.613
SO I'VE TRADED
ONE PRISON FOR ANOTHER?

26:12.613 --> 26:15.882
WELL, AT LEAST THIS ONE
COMES WITH CREATURE COMFORTS.

26:15.882 --> 26:18.351
NOW, ENOUGH WITH THIS.
ENOUGH.

26:18.351 --> 26:20.787
ENOUGH OF THE DISGUSTING
TALK, OKAY?

26:20.787 --> 26:21.988
I'M SURE THAT
IT BOTHERS MELISSA

26:21.988 --> 26:24.658
AS MUCH AS IT BOTHERS ME.

26:26.660 --> 26:28.995
NOW,
WHAT DO YOU THINK, DEAR?

26:31.331 --> 26:33.033
I DON'T THINK.

26:33.033 --> 26:34.167
HMM.

26:34.167 --> 26:36.670
THE DUMB GIRL LEARNS FAST.

26:38.605 --> 26:40.641
OKAY, NOW ENOUGH.

26:41.775 --> 26:45.345
HMM.
ENJOY YOUR FUTURE WIFE, DEAR.

26:52.519 --> 26:55.155
[ Laughing ]
YOU THINK.

27:01.935 --> 27:03.469
[ SIGHS ]

27:07.007 --> 27:09.042
♪♪♪♪

27:12.445 --> 27:14.180
[ Voice breaking ]
I'M SORRY.

27:24.658 --> 27:26.560
JEFFERY, I'M SORRY.

27:33.433 --> 27:35.201
[ SNIFFLES ]

27:36.637 --> 27:38.772
MOVE.
NO.

27:38.772 --> 27:40.006
I SAID MOVE.

27:44.277 --> 27:46.847
I'M SORRY
THAT YOU'RE IN THIS.

27:46.847 --> 27:50.751
I'M SORRY
THAT I'M IN THIS.

27:50.751 --> 27:54.755
I'M SORRY THAT I DIDN'T KNOW
AND I GOT YOU IN THIS.

27:54.755 --> 27:57.524
I'M JUST SORRY.
YOU DON'T DESERVE THIS.

28:00.366 --> 28:01.902
OKAY.

28:01.902 --> 28:04.037
CAN YOU JUST MOVE, PLEASE?

28:04.037 --> 28:07.073
SORRY.
[ SNIFFLES ]

28:12.979 --> 28:16.116
SHE'LL BE ASLEEP IN AN HOUR.

28:16.116 --> 28:17.851
AND SHE ‐‐ MOST TIMES,

28:17.851 --> 28:19.986
IT'S ON THE SOFA
DOWNSTAIRS.

28:19.986 --> 28:23.023
SHE PASSES OUT EVERY NIGHT.

28:23.023 --> 28:26.259
SHE'S SO MISERABLE.

28:26.259 --> 28:30.931
WHEN SHE'S ASLEEP,
YOU CAN LEAVE.

28:30.931 --> 28:32.966
GO TO YOUR FRIEND.
I'LL COVER FOR YOU.

28:35.201 --> 28:37.971
I DON'T WANT YOU
TO DO ANYTHING FOR ME.

28:39.640 --> 28:41.775
EVER.

28:41.775 --> 28:44.244
YOU GOT ME?

28:44.244 --> 28:45.712
YES.

28:48.849 --> 28:50.784
IT'S WRONG, YOU KNOW,

28:50.784 --> 28:53.286
THE WAY
SHE'S TREATING YOU,

28:53.286 --> 28:55.556
THE WAY THAT SHE'S
HOLDING THIS THING OVER MY HEAD

28:55.556 --> 28:56.857
WITH MY FATHER'S MEDICINE.

28:56.857 --> 28:58.458
IT'S EVIL.

29:02.002 --> 29:03.837
AS EVIL AS FORCING ME
TO HAVE SEX WITH YOU

29:03.837 --> 29:05.506
AND YOU GETTING PREGNANT?

29:05.506 --> 29:09.409
YES.
THAT'S EVIL, TOO.

29:09.409 --> 29:12.478
BUT SHE HAS ME
THE WAY THAT SHE HAS YOU.

29:12.478 --> 29:14.715
[ SCOFFS ]
YEAH, RIGHT.

29:14.715 --> 29:17.618
I CAN'T LET
MY FATHER DIE, JEFFERY.

29:17.618 --> 29:19.485
I CAN'T.

29:19.485 --> 29:23.056
HE HAS WORKED SO HARD
HIS WHOLE LIFE.

29:23.056 --> 29:25.425
AND I WAS JUST SUPPOSED
TO FINISH SCHOOL

29:25.425 --> 29:29.663
AND HAVE MONEY
AND HELP THEM WITH THEIR BILLS.

29:31.998 --> 29:35.869
AND NOW THAT HE'S GOTTEN SICK,
WE HAVE NOTHING.

29:35.869 --> 29:38.004
I THOUGHT THAT THIS ‐‐

29:40.140 --> 29:42.576
I THOUGHT THAT THIS SEEMED
LIKE A WAY OUT,

29:42.576 --> 29:45.579
BUT IT'S DEEPER IN.

29:45.579 --> 29:47.581
BUT YOU CAN'T GO TO JAIL.

29:52.452 --> 29:55.255
JAIL?

29:55.255 --> 29:57.558
YEAH.

29:57.558 --> 30:00.026
WHAT DID YOU DO?

30:01.668 --> 30:03.570
MURDERED SOMEONE.

30:07.608 --> 30:08.709
[ SNIFFLES ]

30:08.709 --> 30:10.844
YOU DON'T SEEM SHOCKED.

30:10.844 --> 30:11.912
WITH A MOTHER LIKE THAT,

30:11.912 --> 30:14.280
I'M SURPRISED YOU'RE NOT
A SERIAL KILLER.

30:16.917 --> 30:18.819
YOU THINK THIS IS FUNNY?

30:18.819 --> 30:21.287
NO, I DON'T THINK
YOU'RE TELLING ME THE TRUTH.

30:25.759 --> 30:27.794
YOU'RE NOT KIDDING?

30:30.997 --> 30:32.833
YOU'RE NOT?

30:32.833 --> 30:35.035
NO.

30:36.503 --> 30:37.571
I'M NOT.

30:40.006 --> 30:42.342
YOU SHOULD BE
VERY AFRAID OF ME.

30:42.342 --> 30:45.311
I'M NOT.

30:45.311 --> 30:48.515
DEATH DOESN'T SEEM LIKE
THAT BAD OF AN IDEA.

30:56.890 --> 30:58.825
WHAT MADE YOU DO IT?

31:01.267 --> 31:03.169
I WAS BEING PUSHED.

31:06.006 --> 31:09.576
LIKE YOU'RE BEING PUSHED NOW?

31:09.576 --> 31:12.212
EXACTLY LIKE HOW
I'M BEING PUSHED NOW.

31:15.115 --> 31:18.218
BOBBY SAFEMAN PUSHED ME
IN THE FIFTH GRADE.

31:20.654 --> 31:22.055
I SNAPPED.

31:24.124 --> 31:25.526
SNAPPED.

31:30.997 --> 31:33.199
YOU KNOW, I WAS THINKING.

31:37.203 --> 31:39.305
YOU'RE IN YOUR MOM'S WILL,
RIGHT?

31:43.644 --> 31:47.948
I JUST NEED ENOUGH MONEY
TO TAKE CARE OF MY DAD.

31:50.183 --> 31:51.952
SHE'LL BE ASLEEP SOON.

32:01.868 --> 32:03.970
I'M NOT DOING
ANYTHING TO MY MOM.

32:06.607 --> 32:08.642
I KNOW THAT.
[ SNIFFLES ]

32:08.642 --> 32:09.876
I WAS JUST SAYING,

32:09.876 --> 32:14.881
IF YOU WANTED TO GO SEE
YOUR FRIEND,

32:14.881 --> 32:18.952
YOU JUST HAVE
TO BE BACK BY 4:00 AM.

32:18.952 --> 32:21.254
SHE COMES UPSTAIRS
LIKE CLOCKWORK.

32:25.491 --> 32:27.393
YOU WANT TO GO TO HIM?

32:31.898 --> 32:33.600
[ SIGHS ]

32:35.468 --> 32:36.970
GOOD NIGHT.

32:42.275 --> 32:44.878
[ TELEPHONE RINGS ]

32:44.878 --> 32:45.879
Jim: HELLO?

32:45.879 --> 32:47.447
OSCAR: Mr. Cryer.

32:47.447 --> 32:50.517
WHO IS THIS?
Oscar.

32:50.517 --> 32:51.518
OH, YEAH.

32:51.518 --> 32:53.386
I FOUND YOUR SON'S
ADDRESS.

32:53.386 --> 32:54.521
Do you, now?
YEAH.

32:54.521 --> 32:56.456
[ Chuckles ]
That was quick.

32:56.456 --> 32:58.058
WELL,
HE DIDN'T TRY TO HIDE IT.

32:58.058 --> 32:59.459
WHERE THE HELL IS HE?

32:59.459 --> 33:01.935
HE BOUGHT AN APARTMENT
FOR $3 MILLION.

33:01.935 --> 33:03.604
WAIT A MINUTE.
WHERE? HERE?

33:03.604 --> 33:04.838
YEAH.

33:04.838 --> 33:06.873
WHAT THE HELL?

33:06.873 --> 33:09.009
WELL, IT'S PROBABLY ONLY
WORTH ABOUT 700,000 GRAND.

33:09.009 --> 33:11.311
THAT DAMN KID.

33:11.311 --> 33:12.513
WHAT'S THE ADDRESS, OSCAR?

33:12.513 --> 33:16.249
577 WATERFONT WAY.
APARTMENT NUMBER 9.

33:16.249 --> 33:18.719
YOU MEAN THAT DAMN BUILDING
THAT WE USED TO OWN?

33:18.719 --> 33:19.720
‐YOU DO?
‐Yeah.

33:19.720 --> 33:21.354
WE DEVELOPED IT LAST YEAR.

33:21.354 --> 33:22.923
I'M GOING TO SET UP A MARK.

33:22.923 --> 33:25.358
ALL I COULD FIND OUT IS THAT
HE MOVED THE MONEY OFFSHORE.

33:25.358 --> 33:26.927
AND THAT'S GOING TO BE
A LITTLE HARDER TO ACHIEVE,

33:26.927 --> 33:28.995
BUT THE WAY HE GOT RIPPED OFF
ON THIS APARTMENT,

33:28.995 --> 33:31.497
I'M SURE WE CAN SET UP A SCHEME
THAT HE'LL FALL FOR.

33:31.497 --> 33:33.567
OKAY.

33:33.567 --> 33:35.736
I'M WORKING ON A PLATE
AND SOME PLASTIC RIGHT NOW.

33:35.736 --> 33:37.704
YEAH, OKAY.

33:37.704 --> 33:38.905
I'LL KEEP YOU POSTED.

33:38.905 --> 33:40.106
Hey, thank you.

33:40.106 --> 33:41.842
I GOT TO SAY,
I'M VERY, VERY IMPRESSED.

33:41.842 --> 33:42.943
HASN'T EVEN BEEN AN HOUR.

33:42.943 --> 33:44.811
WELL, I FEEL LIKE
I'M A LITTLE BIT BEHIND.

33:44.811 --> 33:46.880
I GOT TO GO.

33:47.881 --> 33:49.650
WYATT.

33:50.951 --> 33:53.554
[ CELLPHONE BEEPS ]
[ CLEARS THROAT ]

33:53.554 --> 33:54.555
GEORGE: Hello?

33:54.555 --> 33:55.556
GEORGE.
Yeah.

33:55.556 --> 33:56.823
LISTEN, I HAVE A WIRE

33:56.823 --> 33:58.725
AND SOME RECORDING EQUIPMENT
RIGHT HERE AT THE HOUSE.

33:58.725 --> 33:59.793
So, does that mean
you're in?

33:59.793 --> 34:01.768
YEAH.
LISTEN.

34:01.768 --> 34:03.604
I'M GOING TO HELP YOU TRAP
THIS LITTLE TRAMP

34:03.604 --> 34:06.072
IN EXCHANGE FOR ONE THING.

34:06.072 --> 34:07.340
Don't worry.

34:07.340 --> 34:09.643
I'll give you
every photo that I have.

34:09.643 --> 34:11.477
HOW ARE YOU GOING
TO PROSECUTE HER WITHOUT THEM?

34:11.477 --> 34:13.179
Give me one
that you choose.

34:14.781 --> 34:16.617
THEY'RE ALL BAD, GEORGE.

34:16.617 --> 34:20.654
Well, we can modify them.

34:20.654 --> 34:22.188
YOU LISTEN TO ME.

34:22.188 --> 34:23.924
IF I DO THIS,
I WANT THIS GIRL

34:23.924 --> 34:25.892
ONE WAY OR THE OTHER.

34:25.892 --> 34:26.960
Okay.

34:29.062 --> 34:30.631
WHEN CAN YOU START?

34:30.631 --> 34:31.965
Now.

34:31.965 --> 34:33.567
I'll let you know
how it goes.

34:33.567 --> 34:35.802
OKAY.

34:35.802 --> 34:37.237
THANK YOU, GEORGE.

34:37.237 --> 34:39.039
Sure.

34:39.039 --> 34:41.708
[ CELLPHONE BEEPS ]

34:44.811 --> 34:46.847
♪♪♪♪

34:49.583 --> 34:52.152
[ FOOTSTEPS APPROACHING ]

34:52.152 --> 34:54.487
Jim: KATHERYN!
WHAT?

34:54.487 --> 34:57.423
KATHERYN, DID YOU LOAN HANNA
AMANDA'S CAR?

34:57.423 --> 34:59.793
I GAVE IT TO HER.

34:59.793 --> 35:01.568
THAT IS MY DAUGHTER'S CAR.

35:01.568 --> 35:04.004
Shh.

35:04.004 --> 35:05.371
WHAT IS SHE
DOING OUT THERE?

35:05.371 --> 35:07.808
SHE'S ABOUT TO GET
THE HELL OUT OF THAT CAR.

35:07.808 --> 35:09.876
THE TITLE
IS IN HER NAME, JIM.

35:09.876 --> 35:11.411
I GAVE IT TO HER.

35:12.979 --> 35:14.414
WHAT THE HELL IS GOING ON
WITH YOU TWO?

35:20.821 --> 35:21.888
HANNA.
HI.

35:21.888 --> 35:23.624
I DIDN'T KNOW
YOU WERE COMING BY.

35:23.624 --> 35:26.126
I WAS ‐‐
[ SIGHS ]

35:26.126 --> 35:29.095
YOU CANNOT SELL
THIS CAR.

35:32.198 --> 35:33.867
THAT'S NOT WHY I'M HERE.

35:35.268 --> 35:37.604
WHAT'S GOING ON?

35:37.604 --> 35:40.206
I NEED A CRIMINAL LAWYER.

35:40.206 --> 35:42.242
WHAT DID YOU DO NOW?

35:42.242 --> 35:47.180
I DIDN'T DO ANYTHING,
BUT IT'S FOR MY KIDS ‐‐

35:47.180 --> 35:50.517
MY DAUGHTER AND MY SON.

35:52.418 --> 35:53.887
NINE AND BENNY.

35:53.887 --> 35:56.823
CANDACE AND BENNY.

35:58.158 --> 36:00.867
I SAW THE NEWS.

36:00.867 --> 36:02.168
BUT YOU KNOW

36:02.168 --> 36:04.037
HOW MUCH I HATE YOUR ‐‐

36:04.037 --> 36:07.073
DAUGHTER.

36:07.073 --> 36:09.810
BUT SHE'S STILL MY CHILD.

36:09.810 --> 36:14.214
HANNA, I WOULD RATHER
GIVE YOU THIS HOUSE

36:14.214 --> 36:16.950
THAN DO ANYTHING
TO HELP THAT GIRL.

36:16.950 --> 36:19.720
YES, YOU WOULD
END UP HELPING HER,

36:19.720 --> 36:21.522
BUT THE FAVOR IS FOR ME.

36:27.393 --> 36:30.964
[ SIGHS ]

36:30.964 --> 36:32.599
WHAT DOES BENNY HAVE
TO DO WITH THIS?

36:32.599 --> 36:35.135
I CAN'T TELL YOU THAT.

36:37.137 --> 36:39.039
WILL YOU HELP ME?

36:42.743 --> 36:45.879
OKAY.
OKAY.

36:45.879 --> 36:46.913
I'LL MAKE SOME CALLS,

36:46.913 --> 36:51.217
BUT YOU KNOW
VERONICA'S THE BEST.

36:51.217 --> 36:53.419
YEAH, THERE IS NO WAY
THAT'S GONNA HAPPEN.

36:55.889 --> 36:59.059
I'LL CALL MARTY
AND SEE WHAT HE CAN DO.

36:59.059 --> 37:03.469
BUT VERONICA HAS BEATEN HIM
AT EVERY TURN.

37:03.469 --> 37:08.141
AND AS MUCH
AS I HATE THE BITCH,

37:08.141 --> 37:09.976
SHE'S THE BEST.

37:09.976 --> 37:12.378
MS. CRYER?
SORRY.

37:12.378 --> 37:13.379
SHE'S YOUR FRIEND.

37:13.379 --> 37:15.615
MM‐HMM.
WHAT EVER YOU SAY.

37:15.615 --> 37:18.284
SHE'S NOT?

37:18.284 --> 37:20.453
I'LL CALL MARTY
IN THE MORNING.

37:20.453 --> 37:21.822
HE'S ASLEEP NOW.

37:21.822 --> 37:24.224
THANK YOU.

37:25.391 --> 37:26.392
HERE. COME ON.

37:26.392 --> 37:28.228
COME IN THE HOUSE.
MNH‐MNH.

37:29.329 --> 37:32.332
I GOT TO GO BACK
AND BE WITH MY GRANDSON.

37:32.332 --> 37:34.500
OKAY.

37:34.500 --> 37:36.503
DRIVE CAREFULLY.

37:36.503 --> 37:39.205
I'LL CALL YOU
IN THE MORNING.

37:39.205 --> 37:40.206
THANK YOU.

37:40.206 --> 37:41.775
BE SAFE.

37:43.844 --> 37:46.179
♪♪♪♪

37:46.179 --> 37:48.715
[ EXHALES SHARPLY ]

37:48.715 --> 37:50.216
DAMN.
[ LAUGHS ]

37:53.520 --> 37:54.755
ARE YOU OKAY?

37:54.755 --> 37:58.091
YOU ARE...

37:58.091 --> 38:00.260
GIFTED?

38:00.260 --> 38:01.501
WHAT THE HELL WAS THAT?

38:01.501 --> 38:03.970
[ LAUGHS ]

38:03.970 --> 38:06.673
I JUST ENJOY WHAT I DO.

38:06.673 --> 38:09.510
AND WHAT EVER MAN I'M WITH,

38:09.510 --> 38:13.947
I LIKE TO MAKE SURE HE IS
HAVING A WORLD OF PLEASURE.

38:13.947 --> 38:17.217
HOW MANY MEN
HAVE YOU BEEN WITH?

38:17.217 --> 38:20.320
UH, HOW MANY WOMEN
HAVE YOU BEEN WITH?

38:21.287 --> 38:24.024
I ASKED YOU FIRST.

38:24.024 --> 38:25.692
I MEAN, THE ONLY THING
THAT MATTERS

38:25.692 --> 38:29.530
IS THE MAN THAT I'M WITH
AT THE TIME, SO...

38:29.530 --> 38:32.633
SO YOU SEE A LOT OF MEN?

38:32.633 --> 38:35.401
I USED TO.

38:35.401 --> 38:37.070
USED TO?
MM‐HMM.

38:37.070 --> 38:38.739
WHAT'S CHANGED?

38:40.807 --> 38:43.009
I'M GETTING OLDER.

38:43.009 --> 38:45.812
I WANT TO SETTLE DOWN,

38:45.812 --> 38:48.882
HAVE A FAMILY, MAYBE,
IN LIKE 5 YEARS.

38:52.886 --> 38:54.555
WHAT'S YOUR STORY?

38:54.555 --> 38:56.957
NO.

38:56.957 --> 38:58.158
NO, I'M NOT
TELLING YOU THAT.

38:58.158 --> 38:59.459
COME ON. TELL ME.

38:59.459 --> 39:01.167
WHAT'S YOURS?

39:01.167 --> 39:02.903
YOU CAN READ EVERYTHING
ABOUT ME ONLINE.

39:02.903 --> 39:05.438
‐THAT'S NOT THE TRUTH.
‐I AM RUNNING FOR PRESIDENT.

39:05.438 --> 39:09.242
YOU KNOW, REAL STORIES
AREN'T USUALLY IN THE HEADLINES.

39:09.242 --> 39:12.713
I'M SURE A LOT'S GOING ON
UNDERNEATH THAT HEAD OF YOURS.

39:14.114 --> 39:16.783
NO.
THERE'S NOT.

39:16.783 --> 39:18.418
YEAH, THERE IS.

39:20.053 --> 39:24.057
YOU KNOW, THE REALITY
OF THIS IS IT CAN'T WORK.

39:24.057 --> 39:26.459
HMM.

39:26.459 --> 39:28.662
[ SIGHS ]

39:28.662 --> 39:30.764
WHY NOT?

39:30.764 --> 39:31.998
DON'T GET UPSET.

39:31.998 --> 39:33.867
NO, I'M NOT.
I'M JUST LISTENING.

39:33.867 --> 39:36.369
WELL, I MEAN...

39:36.369 --> 39:37.804
I'M GOING TO BE PRESIDENT.

39:37.804 --> 39:39.740
MM‐HMM.

39:39.740 --> 39:43.243
AND I JUST MET YOU,
AND WE END UP IN BED?

39:43.243 --> 39:46.880
MY WIFE WOULD'VE NEVER
HAVE DONE ANYTHING LIKE THIS.

39:46.880 --> 39:48.615
SHE WAS A CONSERVATIVE.

39:48.615 --> 39:50.116
I'M A CONSERVATIVE.

39:51.718 --> 39:54.655
CONSERVATIVES?
OOF.

39:54.655 --> 39:57.958
I HAVE A FEELING
YOU ARE A CLOSET FREAK.

39:57.958 --> 39:59.926
OR WANT TO BE FREAKED.

39:59.926 --> 40:02.636
MAYBE SHE WAS, TOO.

40:05.872 --> 40:07.307
I'M GONNA GO.

40:08.575 --> 40:10.977
GOOD IDEA.

40:15.248 --> 40:16.550
[ SIGHS ]

40:16.550 --> 40:18.685
I'M SORRY ABOUT THIS.

40:18.685 --> 40:20.186
NO PROBLEM.

40:20.186 --> 40:23.056
IF I SAID ANYTHING
WRONG TO YOU...

40:23.056 --> 40:24.858
NO PROBLEM.

40:30.697 --> 40:32.165
THIS WOULD HURT
A LOT OF GOOD PEOPLE

40:32.165 --> 40:34.535
IF THIS WAS TO COME OUT.

40:36.937 --> 40:39.540
ARE YOU APPEALING
TO MY MORAL COMPASS?

40:39.540 --> 40:41.808
YEAH.

40:41.808 --> 40:43.777
WELL, IT POINTS SOUTH,

40:43.777 --> 40:45.178
STRAIGHT TO HELL,
ALL THE TIME.

40:45.178 --> 40:47.113
CANDACE.
YEAH?

40:47.113 --> 40:49.282
PLEASE.

40:49.282 --> 40:51.351
I CAN'T HAVE THIS COME OUT.

40:53.186 --> 40:55.021
WELL...

40:58.491 --> 41:00.466
...I CAN.

41:00.466 --> 41:02.503
♪♪♪♪

41:06.072 --> 41:08.609
[ BOTH MOANING ]

41:27.493 --> 41:29.029
YOU LIKE TO EAVESDROP?

41:29.029 --> 41:31.297
<i>NEXT ON "THE HAVES</i>
<i>AND THE HAVE NOTS"...</i>

41:31.297 --> 41:32.833
SHOULDN'T YOU BE ASHAMED?

41:32.833 --> 41:35.802
NO, DARLING.
I'M HETEROSEXUAL.

41:35.802 --> 41:37.037
I JUST WANT
ONE NIGHT WITH YOU.

41:37.037 --> 41:39.372
I AM NOT COMING
ANYWHERE NEAR YOU.

41:39.372 --> 41:40.473
NAME YOUR PRICE.

41:40.473 --> 41:41.942
WHAT DID YOU DO,
BENJAMIN?

41:41.942 --> 41:44.678
MOM. MOM. MOVE IT.
CALM DOWN.

41:44.678 --> 41:47.280
YOU'RE STUCK WITH ME,
MR. PRESIDENT.

41:47.280 --> 41:49.015
YOU JUST MESSED
WITH THE WRONG FEMALE.

41:49.015 --> 41:51.017
YOU CAN HELP YOURSELF

41:51.017 --> 41:53.787
BY HAVING YOUR WAY
WITH THIS BODY.

41:53.787 --> 41:54.788
WHERE'S SHE AT?!

41:54.788 --> 41:56.156
[ INDISTINCT SHOUTING ]

41:56.156 --> 41:57.257
STOP IT!
